## Steps to Reproduce
1. If default_target_schema is set in config → use it.
2. Else, if the stream name looks like <schema>-<table> (or <db>-<schema>-<table>),
    i.e. it splits on - into 2 or 3 parts → use the second‑to‑last part as the schema name.
3. Else → None.

